person.bio: Akram is a technologist with business acumen who continuously applies his skills toward the betterment of our society. Ambitious problem-solving Web Developer leveraging powerful set of technology skills such as React, React Native and Redux. Always eager to learn and grow and has a genuine interest in leveraging technology for social good.
person.excerpt: Technologist who continuously applies his skills toward the betterment of our society.
